to run those characters.

00:00:35.910 --> 00:00:38.120
Very soon, our posts attracted the attention

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:42.980
of two major players in Islamic State's so-called
cyber caliphate.

00:00:42.980 --> 00:00:47.260
Junaid Hussain is a 21-year-old hacker turned
jihadist from Birmingham

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:51.240
who runs the IS information and recruitment
arm from Syria.

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:55.980
Known as Abu Hussain, he has been identified
by the United States Secret Service

00:00:55.980 --> 00:01:00.350
as a top five target for elimination by drone
strike.

00:01:00.350 --> 00:01:04.489
His wife, Sally Jones, a former punk from
Chatham,

00:01:04.489 --> 00:01:08.120
is now also in Syria, working alongside Junaid

00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:11.740
but dealing with the female IS-supporting
jihadists.

00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:13.540
[Road noise]

00:01:14.120 --> 00:01:19.460
