State want their recruits to attack in the UK.

00:01:19.460 --> 00:01:23.590
We can reveal that this is an entirely new
tactic by Islamic State,

00:01:23.590 --> 00:01:26.910
who originally called for volunteers to join
them. No more.

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:30.860
Sending us details - specially-compiled guidebooks -

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:34.190
they urged our characters to form gangs.

00:01:34.190 --> 00:01:37.060
To create a British Islamic State movement

00:01:37.060 --> 00:01:39.350
over a long period of time.

00:01:39.350 --> 00:01:41.550
The books contain guidance on everything -

00:01:41.550 --> 00:01:44.390
from getting money to building weapons.

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:46.900
This new strategy is a major departure.

00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:50.770
They focus now on so-called lone wolf killers.

00:01:50.770 --> 00:01:55.880
"They're saying the best way to get the kufars,
which are the non-believers,

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:58.220
"is hitting them in their own countries.

00:01:58.220 --> 00:01:59.800
"Hitting them hard."

00:02:00.820 --> 00:02:03.660
