00:02:03.670 --> 00:02:08.479
a second conversation started with our second
character - a girl.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:10.840
Very quickly, Sally Jones came straight to
the point.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:14.529
"She messaged me, saying 'greetings', and
then I replied.

00:02:14.529 --> 00:02:18.329
"And then she asked straight away, 'What do
